#    - Output Directory: (leave empty)
#    - Add all backend environment variables above
#    - Deploy and note the URL
#
# 2. Frontend Deployment:
#    - Create new Vercel project for frontend
#    - Set root directory to: Bidding-Website-master
#    - Update REACT_APP_BACKEND_URL with actual backend URL
#    - Update REACT_APP_FRONTEND_URL with actual frontend URL
#    - Add all frontend environment variables above
#    - Deploy
#
# 3. Update CORS:
#    - Update backend FRONTEND_URL with actual frontend URL
#    - Redeploy backend if necessary
#
